          <msContents>
            <summary>Manuscript comprises a set of rules and instructions for priests performing rites of worship, especially the recitation of prayers, dedicated to the Hindu deity Rudra. Front folio contains a list of works in the same genre (f. 1r), possibly outlining the contents of a larger manuscript or small library.</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="san">In Sanskrit</textLang>
